## Development

### Hot Reload

Changes to YAML files are automatically reloaded in dev mode:
```bash
kdeps run workflow.yaml --dev
```

### Validation

Validate configuration before running:
```bash
kdeps validate workflow.yaml
```

## Deployment

### Package for Docker

1. Package the agent:
   ```bash
   kdeps package .
   ```

2. Build Docker image:
   ```bash
   kdeps build {{name}}-{{version}}.kdeps
   ```

3. Run with Docker:
   ```bash
   docker run -p {{port}}:{{port}} {{name}}:{{version}}
   ```

